snippet: Russia did not advance past the opening round of the EuroBasket women’s tournament in France.
abstract: Russia fails to advance past the opening round of the Euro-Basket women's tournament in France and will miss the world championship for only the fourth time since it began in 1953.
lead_paragraph: Russia did not advance past the opening round of the EuroBasket women’s tournament in France.

headline.main: Russian Women Out of World Championship
